    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of major wear, with all electronics and climate controls functioning as intended. Mechanically, the car is solid, starts reliably, and has a consistent service history. It offers a great balance of reliability and aesthetic appeal for someone looking for a high-quality pre-owned vehicle without the showroom price tag.",
      "price": 34000.0,
