    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear on the upholstery or dashboard. Every mechanical and electronic component functions perfectly, and the car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage. This is a collector-grade example that requires absolutely nothing but a new owner who appreciates perfection.",
