      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating a consistent history of professional servicing, the automobile remains in commendable mechanical and aesthetic order. Its refined performance and preserved interior integrity ensure a sophisticated driving experience. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate the enduring quality and value inherent in this well-preserved example.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
